          <td height="45" VALIGN="TOP" bgcolor="#333333"><div class="topictitle"><table border=0 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0 width=100%>
      <tr>
       <td>
	   <div align="left" class="storytitle">Interview with Nathan Ciprick of Gamics.com</div>
	   <div align="left" class="storyauth">By Nenjin &amp; Ruccus</div>
	   <div align="left" class="storydetail">Apr  5, 2005, 14:01</div>
    
       </td>
       <td align=right valign=top>
      <div align="right" class="newslink"><a class="newslink" href="mailto:?subject=Interview%20with%20Nathan%20Ciprick%20of%20Gamics.com&body=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thesafehouse.org%2Farticles%2Finterviews%2Farticle_17.php">Email&nbsp;this&nbsp;article</a></div>
      <div align="right" class="newslink"><a class="newslink" href="http://www.thesafehouse.org/articles/interviews/printer_17.php">Printer&nbsp;friendly&nbsp;page</a></div>
	  <div align="right" class="newslink"><a class="newslink" href="/cgi-bin/articles/exec/goforum.cgi?id=17&cat=27">Discuss this story</a></div>
	  </td>
      </tr>
     </table></div>
  
  
  </td>
